Package acsse.csc3a.graph.algorithms

Class MSTFeatures

java.lang.Object
acsse.csc3a.graph.algorithms.MSTFeatures
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class MSTFeatures extends Object implements Serializable
A class that efficiently represent an image graph, with (total edge weight, average edge weight, variance of edge weights, edge count) By means of observation these features can be effectively distinguish image classifications. The goal is to use this class as a cheap filter before conducting expensive GED
